item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: Starting a game is a battle for me too man. It might seem like I'm fearless to keep playing, but I realized that nothing will change unless I dive head in to the battlefield. In order to get rid of the fear, I decided to challenge the fear till it became second nature. Thanks for sharing the video! I've added it to the list and will be sure to check it out soon. You can be sure that I will not give up, so no worries there!
item.content:encoded:
Starting a game is a battle for me too man. It might seem like I’m fearless to keep playing, but I realized that nothing will change unless I dive head in to the battlefield. In order to get rid of the fear, I decided to challenge the fear till it became second nature.
Thanks for sharing the video! I’ve added it to the list and will be sure to check it out soon. You can be sure that I will not give up, so no worries there!
